addAlarm2(IBleWriteResponse, IAlarm2DataListListener, Alarm2Setting) - 类 中的方法com.veepoo.protocol.VPOperateManager
  • Add the alarm clock (version two),as you know,we have two version of alarm clock,version one just support 3 group alarm clock,and version two support 20 group alarm clock; this function is for version two,
  • the device most can store 20 group alarm clock,you don't need set alarmId value,the alarmId would be self-distribution by SDK
  • 第2个版本的闹钟,密码验证通过可以拿到第2个版本闹钟功能标志位,来确认设备是否支持功能
  • 最多添加20组, Alarm2Setting对象的alarmId由SDK的内部算法自行分配,开发者即使设置alarmId值也无效
    • Alarm2Setting - com.veepoo.protocol.model.settings中的类
